gentool builds a genesis file for any Cosmos SDK chain from a baseline genesis and CSV-defined accounts, claims, and grants.

Usage:
  gentool [command]

Available Commands:
  completion  Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell
  create      Create a genesis file from a baseline genesis and CSV inputs
  help        Help about any command

Flags:
      --config string   config file (default is ./.gentool.yaml)
  -h, --help            help for gentool
  -v, --version         version for gentool

Use "gentool [command] --help" for more information about a command.
